- `deployment_cost`: trunk / sparse lookup / codebook lookup 等部署端访存
- `total_cost = selection_cost + deployment_cost`
- 当前成本 proxy 以 fused QKV 原始矩阵 `1024 x 4096` 为分母
- 成本硬约束：`total_cost <= 1.5 x (1024 x 4096)`

